# CLAUDE.md

## Workflow

Spec-driven development via bespecific skills:

- kick-off — idea → confirmed `.project/SPEC.md`
- create-spec-issues — spec → GitHub issues / `.project/Tickets/`
- implement-issue — issue → branch, code, PR
- verify-implementation — PR → review comments
- check-pr-comments — feedback → fixes
- merge-pr — approved PR → `develop`
- project-meeting — recurring status meeting, triages `.project/Inbox/`
- generate-branding — on demand: brand guide + assets in `.project/Branding/`

## `.project/`

- `SPEC.md` — confirmed spec
- `Tickets/` — milestone specs, markdown-fallback issues
- `Reports/` — completion reports
- `Inbox/` / `Archive/` — findings awaiting / resolved
- `Knowledge/` — durable learnings by topic
- `Branding/` — brand guide (`BRAND.md`) and generated assets
